This directory contains code specific to SCFT calculations.

Subdirectories:
---------------

iterator/    - classes to implement SCFT iteration algorithms
sweep/       - classes to peform a sweep through parameter space

C++/CUDA source files:
----------------------

ScftThermo.*  - Computes SCFT thermodynamic properties

Makefile and makefile fragments:
--------------------------------

makefile      - makefile for rpg/scft directory tree
sources.mk    - list of source files in rpg/scft (makefile fragment)

Doxygen documentation files:
----------------------------

scft.mod      - defintion of the Rpg_Scft_Module doxygen module

